n="0843a07" ed="T"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0843a07"/><head><date from-iso="+0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="+0907-06-06">唐</date><placeName key="PL000000005408"><placeName>五臺山</placeName><placeName>法華院</placeName></placeName><persName key="A002452">神英</persName>傳</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0843a08"/><persName key="A002452">釋神英</persName>，罔知姓氏<ptr target="#n612"/>，<placeName key="PL000000003047">滄州</placeName>人也。宿緣悟道，丱<lb
ed="T" n="0843a09"/>歲從師，諷誦精勤，日夜匪懈。年當應法受<lb
ed="T" n="0843a10"/>具，後乃<anchor xml:id="beg0843sgsz3"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>枝</sic><corr>仗</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0843sgsz3"/>錫萍遊，尋訪知識。早通玄話，兼<lb
ed="T" n="0843a11"/>擅論經，相次參<persName key="A005612">神會<roleName>禪師</roleName></persName>，謂<persName key="A002452">英</persName>曰：「<ref type="person" target="#A002452">汝</ref>於<placeName key="PL000000005250">五<lb
ed="T" n="0843a12"/>臺山</placeName>有緣，速宜往彼瞻<anchor xml:id="beg0843sgsz4"/>禮<anchor xml:id="end0843sgsz4"/><persName key="A002144">文殊</persName>，兼訪遺<lb
ed="T" n="0843a13"/>跡。」既承指授，以<date from-iso="+0716-07-08" key="j19827621982771" to-iso="+0716-07-17"><name>開元</name>四年六月中旬</date>到<ref type="place" target="#PL000000005250">山</ref><lb
ed="T" n="0843a14"/>瞻<anchor xml:id="beg0843sgsz5"/>禮<anchor xml:id="end0843sgsz5"/>，於僧厨止泊。一日，食畢遊於西林，忽<lb
ed="T" n="0843a15"/>見一院題曰「法華」，<persName key="A002452">英</persName>遂入中，見多寶塔一<lb
ed="T" n="0843a16"/>座，<anchor xml:id="beg0843sgsz7"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>瑋</sic><corr>暐</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0843sgsz7"/>曄繁華，如《法華經》說同也。其四門玉石<lb
ed="T" n="0843a17"/>功德，細妙光彩，神工罕測。後面有「護國仁王<lb
ed="T" n="0843a18"/>樓」<ptr target="#n2681"/>，上有玉石<persName key="A002144">文殊</persName>、<persName key="A003079">普賢</persName>之像。前有三門一十<lb
ed="T" n="0843a19"/>三間，內門兩畔，有行宮道場<ptr target="#n2682"/>，是<persName key="A002144">文殊</persName>、<persName key="A003079">普賢</persName>儀<lb
ed="T" n="0843a20"/>仗。三門外狀<placeName key="PL000000005250">臺山</placeName>十寺<ptr target="#n2683"/>，杳然物外，觀瞻浩蕩，<lb
ed="T" n="0843a21"/>神情恍𢠵。<persName key="A002452">英</persName>試出院，又見眾僧且非恒所<lb
ed="T" n="0843a22"/>見者，而多詭異。疑豫<ptr type="glossary" target="#g45"/>未決，遂出門東行，可<lb
ed="T" n="0843a23"/>三十步，忽聞閉戶鏗然，迴目視之，了無一<lb
ed="T" n="0843a24"/>物。<persName key="A002452">英</persName>乃悲泣曰：「此大聖警悟<ref type="person" target="#A002452">我</ref>邪！於此地<lb
ed="T" n="0843a25"/>必有緣矣。」遂於髣髴多寶塔處結庵而止。<lb
ed="T" n="0843a26"/>乃發願曰：「<ref type="person" target="#A002452">我</ref>依化院建置一所住持。」日居<lb
ed="T" n="0843a27"/>月諸<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1284"/>，信施如林，歸依者眾。遂召工匠，有高價<lb
ed="T" n="0843a28"/>者，誓不酬之<ptr target="#n613"/>。乃於<placeName key="PL000000002348">易州</placeName>千里取乎玉石，用<lb
ed="T" n="0843a29"/>造功德<ptr target="#n2684"/>，細妙光瑩，功侔所見。其壁乃王府<pb ed="T" n="0843b" xml:id="T50.2061.0843b"/><lb
ed="T" n="0843b01"/>友<ptr target="#n3178"/><persName key="A009049">吳道子</persName>之跡，六法<ptr target="#n1370"/>絕妙，為世所尚。此院前<lb
ed="T" n="0843b02"/>後工畢，因號<placeName key="PL000000005408">法華</placeName>耳<ptr target="#n614"/>。<persName key="A002452">英</persName>說法住持，其齊整<lb
ed="T" n="0843b03"/>若剪裁焉。後無疾，召門人囑付而終，春秋<lb
ed="T" n="0843b04"/>七十五。今墳塔存矣。</p>
